  ### Migration Example

  Add a column to store visitor_id:

  ```ruby
  # Rails migration
  class AddMbuzzVisitorIdToOrders < ActiveRecord::Migration[8.0]
    def change
      add_column :orders, :mbuzz_visitor_id, :string
      add_index :orders, :mbuzz_visitor_id
    end
  end
